title: Osho Birthday Celebration 11 December 2010, Oshodham.flv
description:
Video with moments of Osho's Birthday celebration 11 December 2010, in Oshodham, Delhi, India.
In this video at the end Osho is saying: "I was thinking what should I give it to you today, because this is my birthday.I was incarnated into this body on this day. This is the day I saw for the first time the green of the trees and the blue of the skies. This was the day when first time I opened my eyes and saw God alaround.Of course the word God didn't exist at that moment, but what I saw was God.I was thinking what should I give it to you today,then I rememebered a saying of Buddha:
"Sabba danam dhamma danam jinati"-Buddha. The gift of Truth excends all of the gifts. And my Truth is Love
